NAME: KLK10
median_normal: Strongly overexpressed in tumors — KLK10 is known as a cancer-associated kallikrein involved in tumor invasion and metastasis.

NAME: ERLIN1
median_normal: Mild but significant decrease in tumor tissue; may affect ER stress or lipid metabolism.

NAME: LETMD1
median_normal: Highly significant decrease; linked to mitochondrial and metabolic regulation.

NAME: DNAAF6
median_normal: Low overall expression, but significantly higher in tumors — may indicate ciliogenesis disruption.

NAME: ZSWIM7
median_normal: Strongly reduced in tumors; could relate to DNA repair or cell cycle functions.
